---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Dapper Doxie"
  description="Privacy Policy for Dapper Doxie explaining what information we collect, how we use it, and how to contact us."
  keywords="privacy policy, Dapper Doxie privacy, puppy inquiry data"
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Privacy Policy"
    subtitle="How Dapper Doxie collects, uses, and protects your information"
    breadcrumbs={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Privacy Policy' }
    ]}
  />

  <section class="policy-page">
    <div class="policy-container">
      <article class="policy-card">
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 16, 2026</p>
        <p>
          Dapper Doxie respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes what information we collect on our
          website, how we use it, and the choices available to you.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact details you submit through forms, including name, email, phone number, and city/state.</li>
          <li>Puppy preferences and inquiry details you share voluntarily.</li>
          <li>Basic technical information such as browser type, device type, and pages visited.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your inquiry and help you with puppy selection, pickup, or delivery planning.</li>
          <li>To provide updates you requested, such as availability and litter notifications.</li>
          <li>To improve website functionality, user experience, and customer communication quality.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Form Processing and Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          Our website forms are processed through Web3Forms. Information submitted through those forms is transmitted
          securely to deliver your inquiry to Dapper Doxie.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We may use basic cookies or similar technologies to support site performance and understand how visitors use
          our pages. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. We only share information when needed to provide requested services
          (for example, arranging transportation) or when required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We keep inquiry records only as long as reasonably necessary for customer service, compliance, and internal
          documentation purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You may request to review, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us directly.
          We will respond within a reasonable timeframe.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our website is intended for adults interested in puppy adoption. We do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children under 13.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated
          revision date.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have privacy questions, contact Dapper Doxie at
          <a href="mailto:info@dapperdoxie.com">info@dapperdoxie.com</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    background: #F7FAF7;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-family, 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif);
  }

  .policy-container {
    max-width: 940px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .policy-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .last-updated {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #7a6b5e;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .policy-card h2 {
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0.55rem;
    color: #143521;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .policy-card p,
  .policy-card li {
    margin: 0;
    color: #585858;
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  .policy-card ul {
    margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .policy-card a {
    color: #1F5132;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .policy-page {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .policy-card {
      padding: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
